Connect With Us
The Linux Foundation is the organization of choice for
technologists, executives and other open source
professionals who are building durable ecosystems to
accelerate development as well as commercial adoption.
If youre new to open source, looking to step up your
contributions or want to sharpen your technical
skills, we want to hear from you. Similarly, if you have
technology that would benefit from a neutral home
and collaborative development, please contact us.
We invite you to be a part of our community and look
forward to connecting with you.
